::Feline::
She kissed him and closed her eyes.

KitKat::
She listened to him. "So we are now only a group of 5 and no longer a 
force."  she loked down, regretting ever letting this happen.  She 
walked slowly away from him, not wanting him to see her start to cry. 
She hated being weak like this, but it was part of her nature.  
She stopped and wiped her face with her hands.  She turned and looked 
at Drillbit.  "WE have to get them back.  If not, then we have to 
join another group to survive." She hading saying that, but she had 
to realize, the Predacons were gone.
